      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Roll up your sleeves for this fantastic diamond in the rough! This vehicle is the perfect choice for a dedicated hobbyist looking for a rewarding restoration project or someone in need of a valuable parts donor. While it requires substantial mechanical and cosmetic work to get back on the road, it offers a great foundation at a price that's hard to beat!",
