      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to a standard that transcends the typical pre-owned classification. This motorcar remains in pristine, showroom condition, exhibiting a flawless exterior profile and an interior that retains its original factory integrity. Every mechanical and aesthetic detail has been rigorously preserved, ensuring that this vehicle meets the exacting requirements of the most sophisticated enthusiast. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a specimen of uncompromising quality and provenance.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
