      "description": "Presented in impeccable showroom condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, reflects a history of meticulous care and climate-controlled storage. Mechanically indistinguishable from new, this investment-grade example offers a rare opportunity for the discerning collector who demands absolute perfection.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
